    <entry>
      <title>Redis常用命令</title>
      <link href="/2019/03/15/redis-common-commands/"/>
      <url>/2019/03/15/redis-common-commands/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="启动Redis服务"><a href="#启动Redis服务" class="headerlink" title="启动Redis服务"></a>启动Redis服务</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">redis-server redis.conf</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="客户端连接"><a href="#客户端连接" class="headerlink" title="客户端连接"></a>客户端连接</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># -h 为ip -p 为端口 -a 为密码</span><br><span class="line">redis-cli -h xxx -p xxx -a xxx</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="关闭Redis服务"><a href="#关闭Redis服务" class="headerlink" title="关闭Redis服务"></a>关闭Redis服务</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">redis-cli shutdown</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="通用操作"><a href="#通用操作" class="headerlink" title="通用操作"></a>通用操作</h2><h3 id="key值操作"><a href="#key值操作" class="headerlink" title="key值操作"></a>key值操作</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># 获取符合pattern的所有key，当pattern为*时，查询所有的key</span><br><span class="line">keys pattern</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># 删除，可删除多个key</span><br><span class="line">del key [key ...]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># 判断是否key存在，返回存在key的数量，0为不存在</span><br><span class="line">exists key [key ...]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># 设置过期时间，seconds秒 timestamp时间戳 milliseconds毫秒</span><br><span class="line">expire key [seconds | timestamp | milliseconds]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># 删除key对应的过期时间</span><br><span class="line">persist key</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># 返回key值剩余的过期时间，秒表示</span><br><span class="line">ttl key</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># 返回key值剩余的过期时间，毫秒表示</span><br><span class="line">pttl key</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># 返回key对应的类型，返回为：string、list、hash、set、zset</span><br><span class="line">type key</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># 返回随机的key</span><br><span class="line">randomkey</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># 重命名key</span><br><span class="line">rename key newkey</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># 序列化key对应的value值</span><br><span class="line">dump key</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># 移动key到数据库db中</span><br><span class="line">move key db</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># 打印字符串</span><br><span class="line">echo message</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="服务器操作"><a href="#服务器操作" class="headerlink" title="服务器操作"></a>服务器操作</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># 测试连接是否还在</span><br><span class="line">ping</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># 关闭连接</span><br><span class="line">quit</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># 切换指定数据库</span><br><span class="line">select index</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># 查看当前数据库所有key的数量</span><br><span class="line">dbsize</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># 清空当前数据库</span><br><span class="line">flushdb</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># 清除所有数据库</span><br><span class="line">flushall</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="字符串类型"><a href="#字符串类型" class="headerlink" title="字符串类型"></a>字符串类型</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># 设置key对应的值</span><br><span class="line">set key value</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># 获取key对应的值</span><br><span class="line">get key</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># 获取key对应的子字符串，start为开始位置，end为结束位置，字符串位置从0开始，如果位置不存在则以空字符串代替</span><br><span class="line">getrange key start end</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># 给key设置新值，并且返回原来的值，如果key不存在，则返回nil，但是key和其值value是设置成功的</span><br><span class="line">getset key value</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># 获取多个key值</span><br><span class="line">mget key [key ...]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># 设置key值，并且设置他的过期时间</span><br><span class="line">setex key seconds value</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># 当key不存在是，设置key的值</span><br><span class="line">setnx key value</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># 返回key对应的值的长度</span><br><span class="line">strlen key</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># 一次性设置多个key-value组合</span><br><span class="line">mset key value [key value ...]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># 仅当key不存在时，设置value值</span><br><span class="line">msetnx key value [key value ...]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># 和setex相似，这是以毫秒的时间设置key的过期时间</span><br><span class="line">psetex key milliseconds value</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># 将key中存储的数字加一，如果key值对应的value不是int值，报错</span><br><span class="line">incr key</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># 给key值增加指定量increment</span><br><span class="line">incrby key increment</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># 给key值增加指定量的浮点数increment，key的值可以是整数，也可以是小数</span><br><span class="line">incrbyfloat key increment</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># 将key中存储的值减一</span><br><span class="line">decr key</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># 将key中存储的值减去指定的量decrement</span><br><span class="line">decrby key decrement</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># 如果key值存在，将value插入到原值后面，如果key值不存在，则增加key，并将值设置为value</span><br><span class="line">append key value</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="hash命令"><a href="#hash命令" class="headerlink" title="hash命令"></a>hash命令</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># 设置key对应的哈希表的一个键值对</span><br><span class="line">hset key field value</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># 设置key对应的哈希表多个键值对</span><br><span class="line">hmset key field1 value1 [field2 value2 ...]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># 当key对应的哈希表中字段field不存在时，设置值为value</span><br><span class="line">hsetnx key field value</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># 删除key对应的哈希表中一个或多个字段</span><br><span class="line">hdel key field [field ...]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># 查看哈希表key中，是否有指定字段</span><br><span class="line">hexists key field</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
